<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Template</title>
    <style>
      .container {
        width: 55%;
        height: auto;
        border: 3px solid black;
        position: absolute;
        top: 70%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #594FF5;
        width: 100%;
        border-bottom: 3px solid black;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        padding: 10px;
      }

      .header img {
        height: 52px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .content p:first-child {
        font-size: 25px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .content p:nth-child(2) {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .call-to-action {
        position: relative;
      }

      .call-to-action .overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.5px;
        left: 5px;
        width: 100%;
        height: 200%;
        background-color: black;
        z-index: 0;
      }

      .call-to-action .button {
        width: 170px;
        border: 3px solid black;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #ffc34d;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer {
        border-top: 3px solid black;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #d9d9d9;
      }

      .footer .social-icons {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .footer img {
        height: 20px;
        border: 2px solid black;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <%= image_tag attachments["logo.png"].url %>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi, <%= @user.full_name %></p>
        <p>Thank you for creating an account on the<br>London Filmed booking platform.</p>
        <p>Your account manager is <%= @manager.full_name %></p>
        <p>If there is anything you need with, you can<br>get in touch with them at <%= @manager.email %></p>
        <p>Or, feel free to</p>
        <div class="call-to-action">
          <div class="overlay"></div>
          <a class="button" href="<%= @booking_link %>">Book a call</a>
        </div>
        <p>If you're ready to get started</p>
        <p>create a quote for your next event</p>
        <p>Thanks,</p>
        <p>London Filmed</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-icons">
          <%= image_tag attachments["linkedicon.png"].url %>
          <%= image_tag attachments["instagramicon.png"].url %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>